Path: godot/classes/class_pathfollow3d.rst
Summary: Provides the method to correct the transform of a PathFollow3D node based on its rotation mode.
Method: correct_posture(transform: Transform3D, rotation_mode: RotationMode) → Transform3D
Correct the transform. rotation_mode implicitly specifies how posture (forward, up and sideway direction) is calculated.